We've done rhag 1 with around 20 people, and two clerics. This was back in the first couple days of luclin release, so we had no idea what this mob was about, especially how his agro worked. So both our clerics bit it early on, and we had to kill him with druids and shamans healing.<br>
<br>
It becomes a fun fight when you have no clerics to CH you. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
